item.title: Starting A server!
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

If you’d like to apply for a position in someones development then go ahead and post in their topic, if acceptable. There is no point in offering yourself with such a poor application in a separate topic. If you want to start a development team then make a proper topic with correct information and potential media.

Nobody will join a server where the owner doesn’t put effort into anything.
